The components in this directory are adapted from Vercel AI Elements
(https://github.com/vercel/ai-elements), Copyright Vercel, Inc., licensed
under the Apache License, Version 2.0:

    http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0

They were vendored and modified for this project (gestalt token styling,
local primitives instead of shadcn/ui + Radix, local message/tool types
instead of the Vercel AI SDK's, ShikiCode rendering instead of
@streamdown/code). Each file's header notes its upstream source and
divergences. Modifications are licensed under the repository's license.
